preference.name: MEDesignToBomChildAlignmentProperties
preference.preference_description: Specifies the BOM Line properties to be included during alignment between Design and child BOM Line representing that Design under Part assembly. This preference value is only a repository, and it is not to be modified other than by the code itself. Valid values are BOM Line property internal names.
